---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<BaseLayout title={`Prompts - ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="Development prompts and shortcuts for FloodBoy">
	<div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 max-w-4xl">
		<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Development Prompts</h1>
		
		<div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
			<section class="mb-12">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Quick Reference Commands</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
					These short codes help streamline development workflow and maintain consistency across sessions.
				</p>
				
				<div class="space-y-6">
					<div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
						<h3 class="font-mono text-xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">ccc</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">
							<strong>Create Context & Compact</strong> - Saves current session state for future reference
						</p>
						<ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
							<li>Gathers changed files and recent commits</li>
							<li>Exports conversation to markdown</li>
							<li>Creates GitHub context issue</li>
							<li>Compacts conversation for fresh start</li>
						</ul>
					</div>

					<div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
						<h3 class="font-mono text-xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">nnn</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">
							<strong>Next Task Planning</strong> - Smart planning that auto-runs ccc if needed
						</p>
						<ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
							<li>Checks for recent context issues</li>
							<li>Performs deep analysis of codebase</li>
							<li>Creates comprehensive implementation plan</li>
							<li>NO coding - only research and planning</li>
						</ul>
					</div>

					<div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
						<h3 class="font-mono text-xl font-bold text-purple-600 mb-2">lll</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">
							<strong>List Project Status</strong> - Comprehensive project overview
						</p>
						<ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
							<li>Shows open/closed issues</li>
							<li>Lists recent pull requests</li>
							<li>Displays git status</li>
							<li>Provides visual summary</li>
						</ul>
					</div>

					<div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
						<h3 class="font-mono text-xl font-bold text-orange-600 mb-2">rrr</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">
							<strong>Create Retrospective</strong> - Document session learnings
						</p>
						<ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
							<li>Exports full conversation</li>
							<li>Creates detailed retrospective document</li>
							<li>Captures lessons learned</li>
							<li>Updates CLAUDE.md if needed</li>
						</ul>
					</div>

					<div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
						<h3 class="font-mono text-xl font-bold text-red-600 mb-2">/tmux</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">
							<strong>Start Tmux Session</strong> - 3-pane development layout
						</p>
						<ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
							<li>Pane 0: Dev server (pnpm dev)</li>
							<li>Pane 1: General commands</li>
							<li>Pane 2: Git status watch</li>
							<li>Automatic logging enabled</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-12">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Common Development Patterns</h2>
				
				<div class="space-y-6">
					<div class="border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-6">
						<h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Starting a New Feature</h3>
						<ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
							<li>Run <code class="bg-gray-200 px-2 py-1 rounded">nnn</code> to analyze and plan</li>
							<li>Review the created plan issue</li>
							<li>Create feature branch from issue</li>
							<li>Implement following the plan</li>
							<li>Test with build verification</li>
							<li>Create PR with descriptive message</li>
						</ol>
					</div>

					<div class="border-l-4 border-green-500 pl-6">
						<h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Bug Fix Workflow</h3>
						<ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
							<li>Document the bug with screenshots</li>
							<li>Use direct feedback ("worst! why")</li>
							<li>Fix systematically (UI ‚Üí functionality ‚Üí data)</li>
							<li>Test thoroughly before committing</li>
							<li>Create focused PR</li>
						</ol>
					</div>

					<div class="border-l-4 border-purple-500 pl-6">
						<h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Session Management</h3>
						<ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
							<li>Start with <code class="bg-gray-200 px-2 py-1 rounded">/tmux</code> for dev environment</li>
							<li>Use <code class="bg-gray-200 px-2 py-1 rounded">lll</code> to check project state</li>
							<li>Work on tasks with TodoWrite tracking</li>
							<li>End with <code class="bg-gray-200 px-2 py-1 rounded">rrr</code> for retrospective</li>
						</ol>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-12">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Git Commit Format</h2>
				<div class="bg-gray-900 text-white p-6 rounded-lg font-mono text-sm">
					<pre>[type]: [brief description]

- What: [specific changes]
- Why: [motivation]
- Impact: [affected areas]

Closes #[issue-number]

ü§ñ Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.ai/code)

Co-Authored-By: Claude &lt;noreply@anthropic.com&gt;</pre>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-12">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Testing Checklist</h2>
				<div class="bg-yellow-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
					<p class="font-semibold mb-3">Before pushing any changes:</p>
					<ul class="space-y-2">
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<input type="checkbox" class="mt-1 mr-2" disabled />
							<span>Stop dev server in pane 0.0: <code class="bg-gray-200 px-1">Ctrl+C</code></span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<input type="checkbox" class="mt-1 mr-2" disabled />
							<span>Run build in pane 0.1: <code class="bg-gray-200 px-1">pnpm build</code></span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<input type="checkbox" class="mt-1 mr-2" disabled />
							<span>Verify build succeeds with no TypeScript errors</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<input type="checkbox" class="mt-1 mr-2" disabled />
							<span>Restart dev server in pane 0.0: <code class="bg-gray-200 px-1">pnpm dev</code></span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<input type="checkbox" class="mt-1 mr-2" disabled />
							<span>Test all affected pages</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<input type="checkbox" class="mt-1 mr-2" disabled />
							<span>Check browser console (should be zero errors)</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<input type="checkbox" class="mt-1 mr-2" disabled />
							<span>Test mobile responsiveness</span>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Key Principles</h2>
				<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
					<div class="bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
						<h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">üéØ User-Driven Development</h3>
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
							Direct feedback drives immediate improvements. Visual problems get visual solutions.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-green-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
						<h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">üìù Document Everything</h3>
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
							Every session creates artifacts. Knowledge compounds through retrospectives.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-purple-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
						<h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">üîÑ Iterate Rapidly</h3>
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
							Small changes, immediate testing. Build verification before every push.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-orange-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
						<h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">üí° Simplicity Wins</h3>
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
							The best solution is often the simplest. Complexity should be justified.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
		</div>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	code {
		@apply text-sm;
	}
	pre {
		@apply overflow-x-auto;
		white-space: pre;
	}
</style>